snippet.title: Peggle Blast Invades YouTube
snippet.description:
Peggle® Blast has invaded the Internet and is bouncing fun into the lives of Keyboard Cat, Trick Shot Titus, Mishka, and the rest of YouTube.
DOWNLOAD Peggle Blast FREE here:
App Store: http://bit.ly/PeggleBlastApple Google Play: http://bit.ly/PeggleBlastGoogle

Take your best shot with a blend of luck, skill, and joyous thrills in Peggle Blast! Clear the orange pegs as you rack up bonus points, and hit style shots that'll make you smile for weeks. Learn from Peggle Masters and harness their powers to score big in peg-popping challenges. Get Peggle Blast on the App Store or Google Play – and next time you aim for greatness, be sure to aim a little more carefully.
 
For more info, visit http://www.ea.com/peggle-blast or follow us on Facebook and Twitter:
FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/Peggle
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/peggleofficial

Keyboard Cat, related Artwork, and "Fatso's Theme" ©, ℗ and ™ Charlie Schmidt; Used under license.
